en: Lunox allows you to easily perform unit conversions, file conversions, OCR operations, QR operations, HTML-CSS-JS-JSON operations and many other leading operations with the various infrastructure it offers.

Some of What's New and Bug Fixes are listed below:

The Glance screen has been edited.
Added sound effects to mouse events.
Discord page bugs fixed.
GitHub page bugs fixed.
Help page has been prepared.
Added Startup Page to settings.
Translations have been edited.
